reviewText: Even tho this film is not long at all, more like 33min. exact... I found it to be a really good one about a insane-looking clown with a evil kind of laugh! The storyline was rather dark and somewhat quite dispute. Im not saying anymore then that so look this one up.
For my friends again, but they say the enjoyed the movie.  I am happy that you could bring them fun.  Thanks so much.
